snippet.textDisplay:
This video came to my feed after 13 years and sadly after KK passed away. KK is one of those singers who can make feel the emotions genuinely, you cry, smile, feel goosebumps. This is so unfortunate that I won’t be ever able to see him live and that he passed away that way. He didn’t deserve it.
KK, you’ll be always be remembered over the generations about your soulful voice, and amazing personality. You are loved ❤
